              <span>Claude, Codex, Gemini, OpenCode</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[#f4e9df]/80 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#28c840] flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
